      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS000351893_0010"/><hi rend="latintype">Herrn Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb168815" type="place">Sternwartestr. 71</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240">Österreich</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><seg><seg rend="left"><pb facs="HS000351893_0011"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb298443">Kuhrische Nerhrung</rs></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb298441">Hohe Düne bei Nidden</rs></hi></seg></seg></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><pb facs="HS000351893_0010"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb298436">Nidden, Hôtel Herm. Blode</rs> (<rs type="place" ref="#pmb46787">Litauen</rs>) <date>19. VIII.</date></hi></dateline><salute>Sehr verehrter Herr Dr.!</salute></opener><p>Aus dem zauberhaften <rs type="place" ref="#pmb298432"><hi rend="latintype">Nidden</hi></rs>, wohin ich von
               <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12173" subtype="implied">Thomas Manns</rs> eingeladen bin – wir gedenken Ihrer wiederholt
            herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t – ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tatte ich mir Ihnen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te Grüße zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>enden. Stets Ihr ganz ergebner</p><closer><signed>Franz Goldstein</signed></closer></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb12176"/>Herzlich verehrungsvollen Gruß!</p><closer><signed>Thomas Mann.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
